FAQs

Is it good for dry, aging, and sensitive skin?

Yes, the Blissal Exfoliating Antibacterial Shower Towel is designed for dry, aging, and sensitive skin. Our Balanced Exfoliation Technology™ gently exfoliates, stimulates collagen, and improves skin texture without irritation. The Bamboo Charcoal Fibers and Silver Ion materials ensure safe, effective exfoliation, making it ideal for daily use on delicate skin.

Why choose physical exfoliation?

Chemical exfoliants can irritate and dry out sensitive or aging skin. The Blissal towel uses natural physical exfoliation to gently remove dead skin cells, purify pores, and improve product absorption—all without harsh chemicals or irritation.

Measurements of the towel?

Our exfoliating cloth is designed for maximum reach and comfort, measuring 48 inches (122 cm) in length. This extra length makes it easy to reach across your back and other hard-to-reach areas for a thorough, effective exfoliation experience.

How long does it last?

Our exfoliating towel is machine washable, designed to last forever while maintaining its powerful exfoliating benefits from day one. For optimal freshness, we recommend replacing it every 6 months—but for the best skin care results, experts suggest replacing it every 60-90 days. Its durability ensures it outperforms traditional loofahs and brushes.
